gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Green Lake County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, GreenLake_Zoning_2016.gdb. The features included within this geodatabase are 'FLOODPLAIN', 'GENERAL', and 'SHORELAND'.

gmd:purpose.gco:CharacterString: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.

gmd:description.gco:CharacterString: Exported original feature class into a new file geodatabase to maintain the original file format of the data and to conform to UW-Madison's data distribution plan.

The data for this layer was published with multiple feature classes, and the metadata was generated from the 'FLOODPLAIN', 'GENERAL', and 'SHORELAND' layers. The name of the geodatabase was change to GreenLake_Zoning_2016.
